title: Analysis-on-Food-Nutrition-Quality
description: In this project, we explore two datasets that consist of recipes and user interactions. This enables us to investigate cooking trends, recipe complexity, and user preferences.

title: Analysis on important of league of legends
description: In this project, we aimed to explore key in-game metrics to understand performance for each position in League of Legends(LOL). Specifically, we investigated the research question: Which role “carries” (does the best) in their team more often, ADCs (Bot lanes) or Junglers?
